The social card of the resident of the Ivanovo region is recognized as the electronic payment instrument.
Changes provide preservation of a travel privilege in public passenger transport.
Since September 24 the order of the organization of travel privilege of citizens with use of the social card of the resident of the Ivanovo region changes.
As the press service reports the government of Russia across the Ivanovo region, changes provide preservation of a travel privilege in public passenger transport and bring the scheme of mutual settlements under the social card into accord with requirements of the Federal law No. 161 Federal Law "About National Payment Service Provider".
At the same time the social card of the resident of the Ivanovo region is recognized as the electronic payment instrument.
Respectively, conditions of its application change.
So, the limit of replenishment is set not on trips as earlier now, and in an amount of money, with preservation of the winter and summer periods - in the winter no more than 400 rubles, during the summer period - no more than 800 rubles the current month.
Now social card holders on the receipts issued in transport will need to keep track not of quantity of the remained trips, but the rest of money.
The cost of discounted travel for citizens will make 1/2 tariffs, acting at carrier.
The remained half of fare is compensated by the regional budget.
The schedule of replenishment of the social card in cash remains the same - during the period about 24 numbers of the last month on the 23rd day of the current month.
The new order of traveling with the social card will have a number of advantages.
So, there is an opportunity to keep the detailed account of an expenditure of money on the social card to within kopeks.
Besides, there is a possibility of return enlisted, but unspent money.
Let's add also that the scheme of mutual settlements with carriers becomes transparent as now a half of fare is paid by the citizen, and just the same sum is compensated to carrier by the budget.
No fee at loading onto the card of money will be charged.
In turn, Vasily Silkin, the deputy chief of department of road economy and transport of the Ivanovo region, reported that in 2014 in the region more than 33 million trips with use of the social card, in the 2015th - nearly 25 million trips were made.
More than 470 million rubles are provided in the regional budget on providing travel privilege of citizens with use of the social card.
As of September 1 compensation sum on these purposes made more than 312 million rubles.
