Euronews: Mister Meimarakis, welcome to Euronews!
Vangelis Meimarakis: I thank for the invitation.
Euronews: Nine months ago your party suffered crushing defeat, having conceded to the coalition of SYRIZA, but now, judging by polls, "New democracy" was made even to it in popularity.
