Ministry of Transport gave instructions to captains of seaports of the Crimea to provide application of the simplified order of calling of small size, sports sailing and pleasure crafts seaport and an exit of the listed vessels from seaport.
Also Ministry of Transport prepared drafts of orders of the Government of the Russian Federation about the statement of borders of the water area of seaports of the Crimea.
Concerning Yalta and Feodosiya orders are already accepted, the others are in a coordination stage, - noted in the press service of department.
According to Ministry of Transport, concerning the small size vessels used in non-commercial purposes the Republic of Crimea and Sevastopol have to carry out state control, classification and survey, state registration.
