Comfortable rate for investment loans - 10-13%.
According to the experts, the market of financing of small and medium business in January-April of the current year sank for 40%.
What, by your estimates, a situation today?
After panic moods of the end of 2014 - the beginning of 2015 volumes of crediting of SME considerably decreased.
The reason is clear: sharp increase in interest rates.
Crediting under 25-30% per annum was not favorable to anybody.
If earlier the bank could put in the raised rate all the possible problems further, from delays to non-returns, then now it cannot be made: rates already transcendental.
For business the current level of rates on the credits of SME is uncomfortable.
The current level is unacceptable for a considerable part of investment projects from the point of view of their payback.
Level of rates of 10-13% would allow business to invest in a wide range of projects and to form on them attractive profitability.
As far as, by your estimates, demand of businessmen for the credits is satisfied?
After downgrade of the Central Bank of an interest rate the situation improved a little.
Credit resources became more available.
However, on our observations, clients began to apply for the loans much less often.
First of all, business does not understand the prospect of the development and future income.
Today at business one exit: it is necessary to learn to work, being guided by today's economic situation in the country and the region.
It is necessary to keep track more attentively of the current results, to control cash flow.
At the same time in the presence of financial resources it is worth using the new technologies allowing to upgrade the equipment, to reduce costs of production and power supply.
All this, eventually, allows the company to make production of more competitive and to keep business even in an unstable economic situation.
What main tendencies of the market of crediting of SME will become stronger and will influence its development until the end of 2015?
Whether the interest rate will change?
The forecast for decrease in an average rate will depend in many respects on policy of the Central Bank, and now the regulator shows the sequence in a question of decrease in a key interest rate.
However you should not wait for radical falling of the price of the credits for SME.
In the current situation a problem, first of all, is inflation which does necessary the raised interest rate for obtaining the real income.
Besides, the cost of money in Russia will remain high even at decrease in rates of the Central Bank.
If to speak about delay level, then traditionally the companies of small and medium business limited both in opportunities of replenishment of money, and in options of correction of economic behavior, certainly, will represent bigger risk for creditors.
I would not begin to expect essential reduction of a share of the bad credits.
The main reason - the international sanctions and their negative impact on national economy.
