Kiev broke up the atomic union.
Kiev officially issued refusal of Ukraine of cooperation with Russia on completion of the Khmelnitsky nuclear power plant.
The Verkhovnaya Rada on Wednesday from the second attempt nevertheless voted for cancellation of the agreement with Moscow.
Arrangements on completion of the third and fourth blocks were signed in 2010-2012, but it was not succeeded to start implementation of the project.
On Wednesday the Verkhovnaya Rada of Ukraine adopted the law terminating the agreement with the Russian Federation on construction of the third and fourth block concluded in 2010-2012 on the Khmelnitsky nuclear power plant.
It was succeeded to carry out the bill introduced by the government of the country only from the second vote, for the first time he was supported by 210 deputies at a necessary minimum in 226, but then after the revote 234 members of parliament supported the project.
The Khmelnitsky nuclear power plant inititated during the Soviet period on the initial project had to contain four 1 GW power units with pressurized water reactors, but managed to construct only two.
Negotiations with Moscow on completion led to 2010 to the conclusion of the intergovernmental agreement, in 2011-2012 Rada adopted the relevant laws.
As means in the budget of Ukraine were not, it was supposed that it is necessary to build blocks on the credit of the Russian side, but funds were not allocated.
After the revolution in Kiev in February, 2014 and the cooling which followed it in the relations of two countries Kiev began to phase out dealings with Moscow in nuclear sector, having announced the refusal to cooperate on the Khmelnitsky nuclear power plant and on the project of construction in Ukraine of nuclear fuel plant.
Purchases in the Russian Federation of fuel for the operating Ukrainian nuclear power plants (provided about a half from power production in the country) remained the only sphere where the relations remained, as to replace with still Ukrainian National Nuclear Energy Generating Company "Energoatom" the Russian deliveries there is nothing.
With other contractor in Ukraine still finally did not refuse plans of completion of the Khmelnitsky nuclear power plant: in 2014 in Kiev declared negotiations with Czech the Skoda JS.
