The bill of indexation of social pensions taking into account increase in prices is introduced in the Duma.
The bill providing indexation of social pensions annually since February 1 taking into account increase in prices is introduced to the State Duma.
The author of the document - the deputy from Just Russia Aleksandr Lomakin-Rumyantsev - also suggests to carry out additional pension indexing on April 1 if growth rate of a living wage exceeds growth rate of goods prices and service.
Indexation of social pensions, according to the current legislation, is manufactured annually since April 1 taking into account growth rates of a living wage of the pensioner in the Russian Federation for last year.
The bill introduced to the lower house provides introduction of indexation of social pensions taking into account growth rates of consumer prices.
At the same time carrying out the first indexation is postponed to February 1, and the second is carried out on April 1.
