Now in the museum there takes place the exhibition of works of Salvador Dalí and Pablo Picasso.
The man of 1985 of year of birth entered the hall of a sculpture at 14:20.
He at once moved inadequately: spoiled a sculpture, broke windows.
Then it began to move on rooms and soiled blood several works of a constant exposition.
Among them there is a portrait Bail of a brush of Miyervaldis Polis.
According to the president of the Latvian union of artists Igor Dobychin to whom Interfax refers, show-windows were also spoiled.
Police and art experts work at the scene.
The last determine the amount of damages and damage.
Concerning the man criminal case about hooliganism is brought.
In the Latvian union of artists from August 4 to September 27 there takes place the exhibition of works of Picasso and Dali at which more than 200 original works of artists are presented.
The commentator Gennady Orlov is hospitalized in Spain.
On Wednesday the champion of Russia Zenit from St. Petersburg will play the first match of a group stage of the Champions League with Spanish Valencia.
Unfortunately, Gennady Orlov will not be able to comment on a game of Petersburgers.
The commentator of NTV channel Gennady Orlov was hospitalized on Wednesday in one of the Spanish clinics with suspicion of an acute appendicitis.
Inspection will give the answer - whether seventy-year-old Gennady Sergeyevich needs expeditious treatment.
Konstantin Genich will comment on a match.
Zenit acts in group of the Champions League.
His rivals are Spanish Valencia, French Lyon and Belgian Ghent.
